title: South Africa 3 Month Bill Yield
description: South Africa 3 Month Bond Yield was 7.04 percent on Monday November 7, according to over-the-counter interbank yield quotes for this government bond maturity. Historically, the South Africa 3 Month Bill Yield reached an all time high of 15 in October of 2008. This page includes a chart with historical data for South Africa 3M.
